@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>@ViewData["Title"]</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-JcKb8q3iqJ61gNV9KGb8thSsNjpSL0n8PARn9HuZOnIxN0hoP+VmmDGMN5t9UJ0Z" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <style>
        body {
            padding-top: 56px;
            padding-bottom: 3rem;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        }

        .navbar {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
        }

            .navbar .navbar-nav .nav-link {
                color: #000;
            }

                .navbar .navbar-nav .nav-link:hover {
                    color: #007bff;
                }

            .navbar .navbar-brand {
                color: #000;
            }

                .navbar .navbar-brand:hover {
                    color: #007bff;
                }

            .navbar .dropdown-menu {
                background-color: #fff;
            }

                .navbar .dropdown-menu .dropdown-item {
                    color: #000;
                }

                    .navbar .dropdown-menu .dropdown-item:hover {
                        color: #007bff;
                        background-color: #f8f9fa;
                    }

        .footer {
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            line-height: 3rem;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            color: #000;
            border-top: 1px solid #dee2e6;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .content {
            background-color: #fff;
            color: #000;
            border-radius: 5px;
            box-shadow: 0px 0px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            padding: 20px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-sm navbar-light bg-light fixed-top">

    </nav>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="content">
            <h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>
            <p>Use this page to detail your site's privacy policy. Here you can include information about how you collect, use, and protect user data. Make sure to provide clear and comprehensive details to ensure transparency and build trust with your users.</p>

            <h2>Information Collection</h2>
            <p>Describe what information is collected from users, whether it’s personal data, usage data, or other types of information. Include details about how this information is collected, such as through forms, cookies, or other methods.</p>

            <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
            <p>Explain how the collected information is used. This could include purposes like improving the website, sending updates, or for marketing purposes. Be clear about any third parties that may have access to the data.</p>

            <h2>Data Protection</h2>
            <p>Detail the measures you take to protect user information from unauthorized access, disclosure, or misuse. Include information about security protocols, data encryption, and storage practices.</p>

            <h2>Your Rights</h2>
            <p>Inform users about their rights regarding their data. This might include rights to access, correct, or delete their data. Explain how users can exercise these rights and how they can contact you for any requests.</p>

            <h2>Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
            <p>Include a section about how and when changes to the privacy policy will be communicated to users. Mention if you will notify users of significant changes and how they can stay informed.</p>

            <h2>Contact Us</h2>
            <p>Provide contact information for users to reach out with any questions or concerns about the privacy policy. This can include an email address, phone number, or contact form.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <footer class="footer">
        <p>&copy; 2024 Your Company. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>

    <script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-pzjw8f+HoX8Ktv5z+Po0iSfka0V6twP1Au5gE2FndcwY6pYFq3e6e+p2EKzI1zzi" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</body>
</html>